weka.distributed

Class CorrelationMatrixMapTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • weka.distributed.CorrelationMatrixMapTask
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, OptionHandler

    public class CorrelationMatrixMapTask
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, OptionHandler
    A map task that computes partial covariance sums for a covariance/correlation matrix from the data it gets via its processInstance() method. Expects to be initialized with a training header that includes summary meta attributes. Can replace missing values with means or ommit them from the updates.

    $Revision: 11018 $
    Author:
